description: You can use Pick Someone to create a list of names and have it choose one from your list at random.  Ask Pick Someone to add or delete a name and choose someone. You can also hear the list by asking Alexa to ask Pick Someone to list all.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask pick someone to add John
Alexa, ask pick someone to choose
Alexa, ask pick someone to list
name: Pick Someone
shortDescription: Randomly choose someone in your list
